%N A396587 a(n) / (4*n!) is the cubic moment of the Farey series of order n.
%F A396587 a(n) = 4 * n! * Sum_{r in F_n} r^3 where F_n is the Farey series of order n.
%F A396587 a(n) / (4*n!) = 1/2 + (1/4) * Sum_{m=1..n} (phi(m)+J(m,-1)) where phi is the Euler totient and J is the Jordan totient.
